      p Age Groups as per the #{$season} season

      p
        | The FG5s has earned a reputation as a fair and sporting
          event with a high standard of football. The tournament
          is also well known as being very efficiently run and
          organised. In previous years the two day tournament has
          attracted around 140 teams and over 2000 visitors to the ground.


      p
        | Please complete and return the
          attached form along with your
          entry fee of £40 per team. There
          is a £5 discount for entries made
          before March 31st.
      p
        | Please note: fees are non-
          refundable for any entries
          withdrawn after April 1st #{$fives_year}

      p
        | All teams will receive a
          communication confirming their entry. Please contact us
          again if you do not hear from us within a reasonable
          time to confirm your entry.
      p
        | For up to date information visit:<br/>
        span.url
          ' www.theFG5s.co.uk
        ' or
        span.url www.ForestGladeFC.co.uk

      p
        | Please send completed
          applications and entrance
          fee to:
        ul.normal.indented
          li Lee Ashley
          li 3 Grennan Close,
          li Ingrave,
          li Brentwood,
          li Essex
          li CM13 3YD
      p
        ' Or you can register your team for the
          tournament via the official site:
        span.url
          ' www.theFG5s.co.uk
        ' or email:
        span.url  FG5s@forestgladefc.co.uk

